The "Plan North" is the fourth dimension of the "vision" that the Prime Minister intends for Quebec, the vision of the "new economic space", which includes the agreement with France on the labour force, the agreement between Canada and Europe and the agreement with Ontario.
Despite the fact that the opening of the North - Northern Territory on the 49th parallel - the Prime Minister has often mentioned in his statements recently, it has never been the subject of a presentation.
