The same government closes its eyes to torture: little does it matter that this young man is psychologically destroyed in the future, and this is undoubtedly permanent, after so many years of torment.
We don't realize it, but we're witnessing the creeping erosion of our rights, our freedom, and our "democracy", the words that Harper's been throwing around so much and that sound so empty out of his mouth.
